summary: They’re burning all the witches even if you aren’t one... so GO VOTE! Early voting ends November 3rd in the state of Florida,...
caption:
They’re burning all the witches even if you aren’t one… so GO VOTE! Early voting ends November 3rd in the state of Florida, and the polls are OPEN from 7am-7pm! Go out there and make your voice heard!! 🗳 @taylorswift #justvoted https://www.instagram.com/p/BpnZRQtDUjA/?utm_source=ig_tumblr_share&igshid=omq7ctkclnta

My sister and I voted last week during early voting after spending a few days beforehand doing research. Before Taylor made public her stance on the importance of voting, I had been planning to vote regardless. Still, I want to thank @taylorswift for pushing me to do my research on the candidates and amendments on the Florida ballots. NOW IT’S YOUR TURN. TAKE THE TIME, GET OUT THERE, AND GO VOTE!

summary: We've read the impassioned posts, seen the pictures, consumed the information she's bestowed, seen her searching for and sharing...
body:
We’ve read the impassioned posts, seen the pictures, consumed the information she’s bestowed, seen her searching for and sharing other people’s efforts but hearing her talk about the importance of voting is something else in itself.

I haven’t commented on her voting-rallying on tumblr because I’m not from the US, nor do I live in the US. But please, do go and vote. You cannot underestimate how far reaching and disastrous the ripples of the American government are.

Go vote for responsible, empathic representatives that you can hold accountable. Please. You have the chance to change the present. That’s even more imminent than the future.

You have the power to change your local and the larger geopolitical landscape. EXCERCISE IT.
